{"tid":1309868,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[網絡安全] 重要！除左支那VPN之外，仲要提防各款支那 App!","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T07:12:03.000Z","uid":34154,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"edacfd5e9d7e9f09e9bedbe7a368d1fd40b68a54","tid":1309868,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"今日有巴打開Post講到原來支那其實操控緊全球30%嘅VPN服務 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1308194/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1308194/page/1</a>)<br />\n除左要小心支那背景嘅VPN，喺AppStore上面仲有好多app係要小心提防！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWe柒，支那寶就肯定信唔過，但係除此之外仲有好多唔同類型嘅App都係支那背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先用Android嘅好多人都會download <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>第三方keyboard</strong></span>嚟打字，但係你有冇諗過呢D keyboard係咩人開發？我喺Play Store隨手search左三個keyboard app出嚟，scroll落d睇下developer個地址，係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那公司</span></strong>嚟㗎！當然，唔會有人走出嚟認個app個mon住你打過咩字，但係支那人講嘅嘢你真係信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有呢D keyboard嘅developer唔係淨係出keyboard㗎，遊戲呀慳電app呀清理app應有盡有，最近咪先至爆左出嚟話連外藉遊客入境新境都要被逼裝監控App(<a href=\"https://github.com/motherboardgithub/bxaq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fmotherboardgithub%2Fbxaq&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUysmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=c4759c07\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/motherboardgithub/bxaq</a>)，喺新疆有人因為討論移民但係因為被一個偽裝成電話清理app嘅監控程式mon到而入左集中營 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連VPN你以為係安全嘅嘢都有支共嘅爪牙</span></strong>，就更加唔應該信任何支那開發嘅App <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgNZKco.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgNZKco.png&h=e15c4ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8r4aSq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8r4aSq.png&h=08c34f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGGPmY6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGGPmY6.png&h=fe5ca713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇下呢三個keyboard要嘅permission，點解打個字要知道你嘅位置？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你放心支那公司知道你嘅位置？</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3QVP6zF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QVP6zF.png&h=6fe261cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAS3rzG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAS3rzG.png&h=5e29fef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPtNTeG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPtNTeG.png&h=c1ed25c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用iPhone嘅你以為用返Apple原生keyboard就冇事？你免費聽歌嘅時候<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">騰訊與你無處不在</span></strong>呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjdYZLK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjdYZLK.png&h=200c0beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而喺iOS嘅AppStore，個人覺得有一個更嚴重嘅情況，就係有大量個人名義嘅developer，但係明明個app/game根本冇可能由一人之力寫出嚟。而且呢d個人名義嘅developer，冇developer website，係人係鬼冇人知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係喺Google search 返呢 d app/game，原來又係支那嘢嚟嘅屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vuoex5N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuoex5N.png&h=965baa57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eP5ELP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eP5ELP.png&h=18bea8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，就算支那app通過到AppStore審查都好，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>為保障資訊安全都應該要當係特洛伊木馬看待</ins></span></strong>，避之則吉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別喺有去過夢遊嘅巴絲，就更加要小心自己電話裝左嘅app同遊戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3408d224b6ae3c63958501fbb2e1580f1f3c36","tid":1309868,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2adbf0efdc9a9857493f5c0032f321637db540","tid":1309868,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740aad03cfbd2edb5f23604d3c22c9fd2eb4ad58","tid":1309868,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5047d0e5e1c6a2fd1c8ea113ddb996c5719d8c99","tid":1309868,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40881e1cbe8eecb80d729e634de588a6249611e","tid":1309868,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3575d6485a7a9453117803ecec5d7a2bf6183a3e","tid":1309868,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB